These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
City: marseilles, san-francisco, edinburgh, new-york
There 4 different types of food: radish, lettuce, garlic, pepper
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, nurse, teacher, accountant
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, montecristo, game, bongani
 1. the nurse is not to the right of the manager##8
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is not to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##8
 3. the bongani-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the manager is not to the left of the accountant##8
 5. the pall-mall-smoker is not to the right of the pall-mall-smoker##8
 6. the person eating garlic is on the right of the accountant##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##5
 8. the person eating pepper is between the montecristo-smoker and the nurse##2
 9. the bongani-smoker is the person eating garlic##1
10. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
12. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
13. the person eating garlic is not to the left of the bongani-smoker##8
14. the person traveling to san-francisco is the game-smoker##1
15. the person traveling to san-francisco is not the nurse##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| City         | marseilles     | san-francisco   | new-york | edinburgh |
| Food   | lettuce | pepper   | radish   | garlic  |
| Job         | nurse  | teacher  | accountant  | manager |
| Cigar     | pall-mall    | game | montecristo     | bongani    |

