The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, amaryllis, orchid, poppy
 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who's sport is sailing##2
 2. the prince-smoker is not to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##8
 3. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the analyst##3
 4. the baccarat-smoker is not to the right of the person who growspoppy##8
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##8
 6. the freelancer is not to the right of the bongani-smoker##8
 7. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
 8. the person who growsorchid is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
11. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
12. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
13. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the accountant##5
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
15. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
16. the police-officer is on the right of the analyst##1
