 3. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5
 4. the australian is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 5. the prince-smoker is not to the right of the person eating blueberry##8
 6. the polish is not to the left of the person eating broccoli##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
 8. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating apple##1
 9. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
10. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the person eating blueberry is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
12. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
