 1. the person traveling to hamburg is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 3. the fan of disco is the person drinking cola##1
 4. the fan of dubstep is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the fan of dubstep##8
 7. the person traveling to new-york is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the fan of d&b##8
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
13. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
14. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
15. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
