 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 5. the bolivar-smoker is not to the right of the firefighter##8
 6. the person driving the tram is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
 7. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the owner of the rabbit##8
 8. the fisherman is the vegafina-smoker##1
 9. the accountant is not to the left of the owner of the fish##8
10. the baccarat-smoker is not to the left of the bolivar-smoker##8
11. the person driving the ship is between the owner of the fish and the vegafina-smoker##2
12. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
13. the fisherman is not to the right of the vegafina-smoker##8
14. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
