11. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
13. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person who growsmarigold##8
14. the person who growsorchid is not to the right of the person who growsdahlia##8
